      <title>Corne无线分体键盘构建指南</title>
      <link>https://isouthrain.github.io/zh-cn/post/20240328--crone%E6%97%A0%E7%BA%BF%E5%88%86%E4%BD%93%E9%94%AE%E7%9B%98%E6%9E%84%E5%BB%BA%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97--life/</link>
